data.description: Welcome to The Village of Escaya, where modern living meets elegance. This 3-year-old, 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath condo offers seamless open-concept living, equipped with Smart Home technology and builder upgrades, including Tankless Water Heater. Enjoy the convenience of a 2-car garage with extra storage space and direct access into the home, complete with ceiling storage and built-in wall cabinets.   Beyond the interiors, this property is nestled in a vibrant master community offering a plethora of amenities. Relax in the pool area featuring fire pits, BBQ cabanas, kiddie pool, hot tub, and lap pool. Stay fit in the state-of-the-art fitness center or enjoy outdoor activities in playgrounds, parks, walking trails, and a basketball court. The community also houses shops, an elementary school, and scenic hiking trails, ensuring a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Embrace contemporary living – make this exceptional condo your home!Experience modern living and elegance at The Village of Escaya. This 3-year-old, 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath condo redefines convenience and sophistication. With Smart Home technology and builder upgrades, including Tankless Water Heater. it's a contemporary dream. The 2-car garage not only offers extra storage but also provides direct access into the home, complete with ceiling storage and built-in wall cabinets.  But what sets this property apart is its location within a vibrant master community, teeming with amenities. The pool area beckons with fire pits, BBQ cabanas, a kiddie pool, hot tub, and lap pool. For fitness enthusiasts, the state-of-the-art fitness center puts larger gyms to shame. Outdoor lovers will relish playgrounds, parks, walking trails, and a basketball court, all within the community. And let's not forget the convenience of on-site shops, an elementary school, and access to scenic hiking trails. This is truly a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and community.  Don't miss the opportunity to embrace contemporary living in this exceptional condo. Welcome home to The Village of Escaya, where the best of modern living meets elegance and convenience.
